Major Activities in 2005
Major Activities in 2005
page.enlisting:
▪ Presented concerns for the GOES-DCS system at a NOAA ▪ Developed a funding agreement template to enable STIWG agencies to fund the DOMSAT component of the GOES- DCS, in light of new funding requirements. ▪ Coordinated funding from OFCM to pre-pay the DOMSAT ▪ Continued to investigate the needs for a DCP with 2-way satellite communication capabilities. This would enable isolated land and marine based DCP’s to be programmed remotely. A SBIR proposal to conceptually develop a low cost, low power and reliable DCP transceiver was submitted by NOAA/NOS and approved.
